---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SectionHero from '../components/SectionHero.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Work With Me or Invest — Matteo Martignoni"
  description="Brand strategy, investment in innovative startups, Italian residency through the Investor Visa programme."
  lang="en"
>
  <SectionHero
    number="04"
    tagline="Who this is for"
    title="A few good reasons to reach out."
    intro="Three kinds of work. Read to find your context."
  />

  <section class="max-w-5xl mt-12 md:mt-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 md:gap-6 items-stretch">

      <!-- 01 · Brand work -->
      <article class="flex flex-col h-full rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100/60 p-7 md:p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-sage-100">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-5">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-terracotta-900 tabular-nums leading-none">01</span>
          <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 leading-snug">Brand Directors · CEOs · CMOs</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium text-ink-900 mb-4 leading-snug">
          The brand work I know best.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Brand strategy, repositioning, category development, distribution,
            retail performance, European market entry.
          </p>
          <p>
            Twenty-five years with Diesel, Aēsop, Eastpak, Reflex, and the
            companies I founded.
          </p>
          <p>The problems tend to repeat. The solutions rarely do.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6">
          <a href="mailto:mm@matteomartignoni.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-terracotta-900 hover:text-terracotta-700 transition-colors duration-200">
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            <span>mm@matteomartignoni.com</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 02 · Investors -->
      <article class="flex flex-col h-full rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100/60 p-7 md:p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-sage-100">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-5">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-terracotta-900 tabular-nums leading-none">02</span>
          <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 leading-snug">Investors · Business Angels · Funds</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium text-ink-900 mb-4 leading-snug">
          Two companies worth a closer look.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            <a href="https://novaexperience.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta-900 underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 hover:text-terracotta-700 transition-colors duration-200">NOVA</a> is an AI experience company building a proprietary platform
            for museums and cultural institutions. Officina degli Estratti
            develops high-end cosmetic ingredients from certified Parmesan
            animal byproducts, with an AI-driven quality and standardisation
            platform.
          </p>
          <p>
            Both have structured business plans and a clear path forward.
            Both are registered as Italian innovative startups.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are looking for partners who can strengthen our governance,
            not only provide capital. If the work interests you, I am open
            to a conversation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6">
          <a href="mailto:matteo@novaexperience.ai"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-terracotta-900 hover:text-terracotta-700 transition-colors duration-200">
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            <span>matteo@novaexperience.ai</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- 03 · Golden Visa -->
      <article class="flex flex-col h-full rounded-2xl border border-warm-200 bg-warm-100/60 p-7 md:p-8 transition-colors duration-200 hover:border-sage-100">
        <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-5">
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-terracotta-900 tabular-nums leading-none">03</span>
          <span class="text-[0.7rem] uppercase tracking-widest text-ink-500 leading-snug">Extra-EU Investors</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-medium text-ink-900 mb-4 leading-snug">
          Residency through innovation.
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            The <a href="https://investorvisa.mise.gov.it/images/documenti/Investor_Visa_for_Italy_Policy_guidance_ENG_19_07_2021.pdf#page=1.00&amp;gsr=0" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-terracotta-900 underline decoration-1 underline-offset-2 hover:text-terracotta-700 transition-colors duration-200">Italian government's Investor Visa</a> programme allows
            extra-EU nationals to apply for an Italian residency permit
            through a qualifying investment in an Italian innovative startup.
          </p>
          <p>
            Both NOVA and Officina degli Estratti are structured to qualify.
            If you are exploring this route, an investment in either company
            could open that path.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-auto pt-6">
          <a href="mailto:mm@matteomartignoni.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-terracotta-900 hover:text-terracotta-700 transition-colors duration-200">
            <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            <span>mm@matteomartignoni.com</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
